, 'Pertuzumab, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Porfimer sodium, Aflibercept, Trastuzumab, Anagrelide, Venetoclax, Hydroxyurea, More', 'Teniposide', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/43377/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
