miting.', 'Synergism', 'Anastrozole, Fulvestrant, Relugolix, Degarelix, Exemestane, Diethylstilbestrol, Histrelin, Megestrol acetate, Leuprolide, Medroxyprogesterone acetate, Triptorelin, Ethinylestradiol', 'Imatinib, Dabrafenib, Dacomitinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, Regorafenib, Alpelisib, Erlotinib, Ponatinib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/43513/', '[1] "Product Information. Zydelig (idelalisib)." Gilead Sciences, Foster City, CA.', 1767369485);
